            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EIsaiah%2012%3A1-14%3A32%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_12_1%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EIsaiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ESongs%20of%20Praise%20for%20Salvation%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20that%20day%20you%20will%20sing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20praise%20you%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYou%20were%20angry%20with%20me%2C%20but%20not%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ENow%20you%20comfort%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_12_2%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESee%2C%20God%20has%20come%20to%20save%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%20will%20trust%20in%20him%20and%20not%20be%20afraid.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3EGod%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20my%20strength%20and%20my%20song%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehe%20has%20given%20me%20victory.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_12_3%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EWith%20joy%20you%20will%20drink%20deeply%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efrom%20the%20fountain%20of%20salvation!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_12_4%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20that%20wonderful%20day%20you%20will%20sing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BThank%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E!%20Praise%20his%20name!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ETell%20the%20nations%20what%20he%20has%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ELet%20them%20know%20how%20mighty%20he%20is!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_12_5%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3ESing%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20for%20he%20has%20done%20wonderful%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EMake%20known%20his%20praise%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_12_6%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ELet%20all%20the%20people%20of%20Jerusalem%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EZion.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20shout%20his%20praise%20with%20joy!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EFor%20great%20is%20the%20Holy%20One%20of%20Israel%20who%20lives%20among%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_13_1%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EIsaiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Message%20about%20Babylon%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EIsaiah%20son%20of%20Amoz%20received%20this%20message%20concerning%20the%20destruction%20of%20Babylon%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_13_2%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BRaise%20a%20signal%20flag%20on%20a%20bare%20hilltop.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ECall%20up%20an%20army%20against%20Babylon.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EWave%20your%20hand%20to%20encourage%20them%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eas%20they%20march%20into%20the%20palaces%20of%20the%20high%20and%20mighty.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_13_3%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EI%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20dedicated%20these%20soldiers%20for%20this%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EYes%2C%20I%20have%20called%20mighty%20warriors%20to%20express%20my%20anger%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20they%20will%20rejoice%20when%20I%20am%20exalted.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_13_4%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EHear%20the%20noise%20on%20the%20mountains!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EListen%2C%20as%20the%20vast%20armies%20march!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EIt%20is%20the%20noise%20and%20shouting%20of%20many%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%20has%20called%20this%20army%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_13_5%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20come%20from%20distant%20countries%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efr